      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2023R1 is a commercially supported solver with a documented software quality assurance plan. Version control, release notes, and a regression test suite are available. No custom solver modifications were made. Level 2 achieved and meets the required level for MRL 2."
    },
    {
