      "rationale": "Use error assessment is scoped out at MRL 2 for this COU. The model is operated by trained CFD engineers following a documented simulation protocol. Peer review of simulation setup was conducted internally. Formal use error quantification is not required at this model risk level per ASME V&V 40 Table 3."
    },
    {
      "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/factor/model-form-001",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Model form",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorStatus": "scoped-out",
      "rationale": "Model form assessment (turbulence model selection, hemolysis constitutive model justification) is scoped out at MRL 2. The k-omega SST turbulence model and Giersiepen-Wurzinger hemolysis model are industry-standard selections for blood pump CFD supported by published literature. Formal model form uncertainty quantification is not required at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 credibility requirements."
    },
    {
