      "rationale": "Test sample characterization (e.g., device-to-device geometric variability) is scoped out at MRL 2. The FDA generic centrifugal pump is a reference geometry with tightly controlled manufacturing tolerances. The validation experiments used a single physical specimen per the FDA reference pump protocol, which is acceptable at MRL 2 for this COU."
